/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n150mins<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我adverage 45mins <br />\n未試過150mins 就算塞車都係最多一個半鐘<br />\n最緊要check 左邊條路塞車先好行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 日日揸車番觀塘"},{"pid":"1f0b2877a883c1113388c3da319e749845677c49","tid":306122,"uid":71358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:31:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>深井去九龍東<br />\n揸車：35-150 min, average 60 min, 視乎塞車程度<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n150mins<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我adverage 45mins <br />\n未試過150mins 就算塞車都係最多一個半鐘<br />\n最緊要check 左邊條路塞車先好行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 日日揸車番觀塘</blockquote><br />\n150 min 係上次打風，成粒鐘都上唔到龍翔道<br />\n35min=唔塞<br />\n45-60 min=少少塞<br />\n60-90 min=撞咗/壞車<br />\n90 min 以上=打風<br />\n<br />\n我都係日日揸....好想轉工....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985d7a9cb441a29f2ecf2ce096fbd1da731d5824","tid":306122,"uid":15157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:34:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>深井去九龍東<br />\n揸車：35-150 min, average 60 min, 視乎塞車程度<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n150mins<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我adverage 45mins <br />\n未試過150mins 就算塞車都係最多一個半鐘<br />\n最緊要check 左邊條路塞車先好行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 日日揸車番觀塘</blockquote><br />\n150 min 係上次打風，成粒鐘都上唔到龍翔道<br />\n35min=唔塞<br />\n45-60 min=少少塞<br />\n60-90 min=撞咗/壞車<br />\n90 min 以上=打風<br />\n<br />\n我都係日日揸....好想轉工....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n通常我盡量唔行龍翔道 因為一定塞 <br />\n行紅磡果邊過時間差唔多 但無咁塞<br />\n如果2條路都塞死就比多少少錢經沙田過<br />\n如果九龍大塞車+深井位塞死唔郁就行粉嶺再經沙田過"},{"pid":"71edff8b94d705df7e26c0eae4c7beef8be25b7a","tid":306122,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:37:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>深井去九龍東<br />\n揸車：35-150 min, average 60 min, 視乎塞車程度<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n150mins<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我adverage 45mins <br />\n未試過150mins 就算塞車都係最多一個半鐘<br />\n最緊要check 左邊條路塞車先好行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 日日揸車番觀塘</blockquote><br />\n150 min 係上次打風，成粒鐘都上唔到龍翔道<br />\n35min=唔塞<br />\n45-60 min=少少塞<br />\n60-90 min=撞咗/壞車<br />\n90 min 以上=打風<br />\n<br />\n我都係日日揸....好想轉工....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n通常我盡量唔行龍翔道 因為一定塞 <br />\n行<span style=\"color: red;\">紅磡</span>果邊過時間差唔多 但無咁塞<br />\n如果2條路都塞死就比多少少錢經沙田過<br />\n如果九龍大塞車+深井位塞死唔郁就行粉嶺再經沙田過</blockquote><br />\n點行？"},{"pid":"21cade81688b6edb158c54906956de18737796e0","tid":306122,"uid":71358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:44:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>深井去九龍東<br />\n揸車：35-150 min, average 60 min, 視乎塞車程度<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n150mins<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif