2T16:21:00.000Z","msg":"住慣左其實都覺得幾方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2876fd89ff37b4c1cb3d315c3d9c010663fe336","tid":306122,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:48:47.000Z","msg":"深井撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d738715c4fabcd46b4e696671ad23c80035d464f","tid":306122,"uid":50535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:51:32.000Z","msg":"我住浪翠8年 返觀塘<br />\n呢幾年多左人 所以要早出門口 <br />\n我7點上出荃灣 到荃灣轉40號<br />\n到觀塘8:20 左右 <br />\n有時到彩虹會塞一陣<br />\n當然可以到荃灣地鐵 會快 但貴<br />\n巴士有轉乘$10到觀塘"},{"pid":"5b035cdf16fcdec18fa6efcc30140c1ecf4a0c8e","tid":306122,"uid":15464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:44:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企有車就好<br />\n入面冇公屋得私人樓村屋<br />\n冇d阿差同唔多大陸人<br />\n風涼水冷<br />\n但冇車好煩要坐20mins小巴出荃灣地鐡站</blockquote><br />\n洗鬼20咩 10分鐘咩都到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4377dec97059ad801878ccbc58d349374d7e00d6","tid":306122,"uid":27221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:51:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要買野方便 成日出街食既就深井<br />\n想易d 搭車 清淨d就青龍頭<br />\n交通唔算唔方便 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">出荃灣美孚20分鐘 圓方30分鐘 上環35分鐘 </span><br />\n旺角佐敦荃灣元朗銅鑼灣都有通宵van 經深井</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n揸車? 西隧好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3fbe409b629b85853378b1b7c1cb3eeedf44c31","tid":306122,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:02:42.000Z","msg":"深井基本超市食肆都有<br />\n有a車去機場<br />\n30分鐘左右到t1<br />\n仲有得差電<br />\n好多空姐住個頭<br />\n<br />\n青龍頭van 荃灣例牌排長龍<br />\n不過個邊夠靜<br />\n又有個海灘<br />\n<br />\n睇你鐘意咩生活"}]}